  81. ‌let clear_part = function
  82.   | Partial_structure s -> Partial_structure (cenv.structure cenv s)
  83.   | Partial_structure_item s ->
  84.       Partial_structure_item (cenv.structure_item cenv s)
  85.   | Partial_expression e -> Partial_expression (cenv.expr cenv e)
  86.   | Partial_pattern (category, p) -> Partial_pattern (category, cenv.pat cenv p)
  87.   | Partial_class_expr ce -> Partial_class_expr (cenv.class_expr cenv ce)
  88.   | Partial_signature s -> Partial_signature (cenv.signature cenv s)
  89.   | Partial_signature_item s ->
  90.       Partial_signature_item (cenv.signature_item cenv s)
  91.   | Partial_module_type s -> Partial_module_type (cenv.module_type cenv s)

  93. ‌let clear_env binary_annots =
  94.   if need_to_clear_env then
  95.     match binary_annots with
  96.     | Implementation s -> Implementation (cenv.structure cenv s)
  97.     | Interface s -> Interface (cenv.signature cenv s)
  98.     | Packed _ -> binary_annots
  99.     | Partial_implementation array ->
  100.         Partial_implementation (Array.map clear_part array)
  101.     | Partial_interface array ->
  102.         Partial_interface (Array.map clear_part array)

  104.   else binary_annots

  106. exception Error of error

  114. ‌let read filename =
  115. (*  Printf.fprintf stderr "Cmt_format.read %s\n%!" filename; *)
  116.   let ic = open_in_bin filename in
  117.   Misc.try_finally
  118.     ~always:(fun () -> close_in ic)
  119.     (fun () ->
  120.        let magic_number = read_magic_number ic in
  121.        let cmi, cmt =
  122.          if magic_number = Config.cmt_magic_number then
  123.            None, Some (input_cmt ic)
  124.          else if magic_number = Config.cmi_magic_number then
  125.            let cmi = Cmi_format.input_cmi ic in
  126.            let cmt = try
  127.                let magic_number = read_magic_number ic in
  128.                if magic_number = Config.cmt_magic_number then
  129.                  let cmt = input_cmt ic in
  130.                  Some cmt
  131.                else None
  132.              with _ -> None
  133.            in
  134.            Some cmi, cmt
  135.          else
  136.            raise(Cmi_format.Error(Cmi_format.Not_an_interface filename))
  137.        in
  138.        cmi, cmt
  139.     )

  167. ‌let save_cmt filename modname binary_annots sourcefile initial_env cmi shape =
  168.   if !Clflags.binary_annotations && not !Clflags.print_types then begin
  169.     Misc.output_to_file_via_temporary
  170.        ~mode:[Open_binary] filename
  171.        (fun temp_file_name oc ->
  172.          let this_crc =
  173.            match cmi with
  174.            | None -> None
  175.            | Some cmi -> Some (output_cmi temp_file_name oc cmi)
  176.          in
  177.          let source_digest = Option.map Digest.file sourcefile in
  178.          let cmt = {
  179.            cmt_modname = modname;
  180.            cmt_annots = clear_env binary_annots;
  181.            cmt_value_dependencies = !value_deps;
  182.            cmt_comments = Lexer.comments ();
  183.            cmt_args = Sys.argv;
  184.            cmt_sourcefile = sourcefile;
  185.            cmt_builddir = Location.rewrite_absolute_path (Sys.getcwd ());
  186.            cmt_loadpath = Load_path.get_paths ();
  187.            cmt_source_digest = source_digest;
  188.            cmt_initial_env = if need_to_clear_env then
  189.                keep_only_summary initial_env else initial_env;
  190.            cmt_imports = List.sort compare (Env.imports ());
  191.            cmt_interface_digest = this_crc;
  192.            cmt_use_summaries = need_to_clear_env;
  193.            cmt_uid_to_loc = Env.get_uid_to_loc_tbl ();
  194.            cmt_impl_shape = shape;
  195.          } in
  196.          output_cmt oc cmt)
  197.   end;
  198.   clear ()
